quotations.quotation: "We are extremely thrilled to celebrate the grand opening of Fairmont Jakarta," said Carlos Monterde, general manager, Fairmont Jakarta. "Today is a momentous occasion for the hotel and the Fairmont brand and we truly believe that the hotel is the jewel of this city. Aside from offering luxurious accommodation, exciting dining and cocktail options, we are also THE lifestyle destination for Jakarta residents. With each space in the hotel providing a unique experience combined with Fairmont’s signature hospitality, we aim to transform every moment into unforgettable memories for our guests."

url.title: Fairmont Jakarta marks grand opening with gala event
